{"type":null,"faqId":22396,"title":"手机微信推片有什么用，如何使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.35416666in;margin-top:0.083333336in;margin-bottom:0.090277776in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"storage_1_sec8_p1\"><a name=\"sec8_p2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_7_3_8_3_1_1\"><a name=\"gen_id1_7_3_8_3_1_2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_7_3_8_3_1_3\"></a></a></a></a></a><span>手机微信推片指的是用户可以通过添加盒子的微信公众号，在微信公众号上搜索节目，并将节目推送到华为盒子上播放。具体操作如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">华为荣耀盒子</span><span>公众号</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74428\" style=\"width:1.3493055in;height:1.3493055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74429\" style=\"width:0.17847222in;height:0.19722222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>您还可以进入华为盒子“</span><span class=\"s1\">应用 &gt; 帮助 &gt; 使用技巧</span><span>”，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">创意遥控器，使用更有趣</span><span>”。查看到该二维码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式一：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子的微信公众号。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">2  </span><span>打开微信公众号的对话框，输入您想看的节目名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">3  </span><span>在收到的回复中，点击节目图片。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">4  </span><span>在打开的节目详情页面中，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">推送到电视</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，电视将播放该节目。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式二：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子的微信公众号。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">2  </span><span>打开微信公众号的对话框，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">应用 &gt; 节目导航</span><span>”</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">3  </span><span>在打开的节目导航中选择您想看的节目，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">推送到电视</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，电视将播放该节目。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":243,"faqType":"本地播放","useful":5,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6276","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Local-Storage-Play","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628512000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":64,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"M330,MediaQ M330,华为盒子,微信,微信遥控,微信推片,手机","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}